          <content src="text/part0220_split_009.html"/>
        </navPoint>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_499" playOrder="431">
          <navLabel>
            <text>蜂毒，可调治关节炎、荨麻疹和哮喘</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0220_split_010.html"/>
        </navPoint>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_500" playOrder="432">
          <navLabel>
            <text>吃对花粉，保肝、抗衰老</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0220_split_011.html"/>
        </navPoint>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_501" playOrder="433">
          <navLabel>
            <text>“春深无客到，一路落松花”——松花粉美容、延年、强身</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0220_split_012.html"/>
        </navPoint>
      </navPoint>
      <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_502" playOrder="434">
        <navLabel>
          <text>第五章：泡菜、腌菜之美</text>
        </navLabel>
        <content src="text/part0221_split_000.html"/>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_503" playOrder="435">
          <navLabel>
            <text>泡菜，有新鲜蔬菜所不具备的功效</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0222_split_000.html"/>
        </navPoint>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_504" playOrder="436">
          <navLabel>
            <text>药食同源的泡菜二宝——洋姜和螺丝菜</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0222_split_001.html"/>
        </navPoint>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_505" playOrder="437">
          <navLabel>
            <text>酸盐菜，开胃和胃、散寒祛湿</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0222_split_002.html"/>
        </navPoint>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_506" playOrder="438">
          <navLabel>
            <text>下饭又补肾，要数酸豇豆</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0222_split_003.html"/>
        </navPoint>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_507" playOrder="439">
          <navLabel>
            <text>一家之政观于齑——主妇会做腌菜是持家本领</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0222_split_004.html"/>
        </navPoint>
      </navPoint>
      <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_508" playOrder="440">
        <navLabel>
          <text>第六章：只有投资健康，才有终生回报</text>
        </navLabel>
        <content src="text/part0223_split_000.html"/>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_509" playOrder="441">
          <navLabel>
            <text>只有投资健康，才有终生回报</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0224_split_000.html"/>
        </navPoint>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_510" playOrder="442">
          <navLabel>
            <text>在吃下每一种食物之前，请想十年后</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0224_split_001.html"/>
        </navPoint>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_511" playOrder="443">
          <navLabel>
            <text>防止“毒从口入”，比中了毒才去补救更好</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0224_split_002.html"/>
        </navPoint>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_512" playOrder="444">
          <navLabel>
            <text>没有什么补品是适合所有人的</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0224_split_003.html"/>
        </navPoint>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_513" playOrder="445">
          <navLabel>
            <text>在身体需要的时候吃饭，是春雨贵如油</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0224_split_004.html"/>
        </navPoint>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_514" playOrder="446">
          <navLabel>
            <text>分清人体体质，一补一个准</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0224_split_005.html"/>
        </navPoint>
        <navPoint class="chapter" id="num_515" playOrder="447">
          <navLabel>
            <text>男怕伤肝，女怕伤肾</text>
          </navLabel>
          <content src="text/part0224_split_006.html"/>
        </navPoint>
      </navPoint>
    </navPoint>
  </navMap>
</ncx>
